  <notes>
    Parallels task 051. Once this lands, UDG PCF has no remaining consumers — safe to retire in task 053.

    Closeout (2026-06-04): Closed as ✅¹ no-op. Task 050 audit established that DashboardPage
    was never on UDG — it uses Fluent v9 `<DataGrid>` directly from `@fluentui/react-components`.
    The original POML premise traced back to a misleading file-level docblock comment at
    DashboardPage.tsx:405-406 that *documented a design choice not to use UDG* but was read as
    if DashboardPage was on UDG. The comment was doubly stale (also referenced a defunct
    `RecentActivityGrid` sibling component). Action this task: removed those 2 lines from
    DashboardPage.tsx; preserved the ADR-021 dark-mode comment above. No migration code
    changes; no screenshots required. Full rationale in
    `notes/drafts/052-deviations.md`. Downstream: task 053 can proceed immediately
    (no UDG consumers remain); task 054 UAT shrinks (no DashboardPage visual diff needed).
  </notes>

